### Videos
- [The largest historical investigation about eastern Ukraine](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_XG6RU2vYsg) (Реальна Історія) — The video directly addresses the debunking of Russian imperial myths and propaganda regarding Ukrainian territories ('ісконно-руський Донбас'), which aligns perfectly with the module's core theme of colonization and myths in Southern Ukraine, particularly the 'Міф про 'Новоросію'' section. While geographically focused on Donbas (Eastern Ukraine), the historical narrative and decolonization perspective are directly applicable to the module's objectives.

